Package: palap
Title: Provides reflective colour palettes
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Nicholas",
           family = "Tierney",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "nicholas.tierney@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-1460-8722"))
Description: Reflective colour palettes can be used in specific cases when 
  you need values tha are above and below the middle point that have different
  values, but similar meaning. For example, the first and third quantiles. You
  can think of reflective colour palettes as a combination of sequential and
  diverging colour palettes.
